## ğŸ”§ Installation Guide

Install Nmap on various systems:

### Ubuntu / Debian:
```bash
sudo apt update && sudo apt install nmap -y
```

### CentOS / RHEL:
```bash
sudo yum install nmap -y
```

### Arch Linux:
```bash
sudo pacman -S nmap
```

### macOS (via Homebrew):
```bash
brew install nmap
```

