## ğŸŒ Real-World Use Cases

### âœ… Scan a Subnet for Active Devices:
```bash
nmap -sn 192.168.3.0/24
```
> âœ”ï¸ Use for host discovery in local networks.

### âœ… Vulnerability Scanning with NSE:
```bash
nmap --script vuln 192.168.3.100
```
> âœ”ï¸ Great for red teamers auditing systems.

### âœ… Find All Open Ports on a Server:
```bash
nmap -p- -T4 192.168.3.20
```

